query:
INSERT INTO execution_process_logs (execution_id, logs, byte_size, inserted_at)
               VALUES ($1, $2, $3, datetime('now', 'subsec'))
               ON CONFLICT (execution_id) DO UPDATE
               SET logs = logs || $2,
                   byte_size = byte_size + $3,
                   inserted_at = datetime('now', 'subsec')
